    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapy doesn't really change the fact that the core of me is missing. it's like... if the music was the soul, and the music is dead, then what am i even preserving here? i'm just a biological machine going through the motions. it feels so pointless to keep maintaining a body that has nothing left to offer.",
